This paper is about natural language parsing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the evaluation of parsing systems, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI, cs.LG). Additionally, the development of new evaluation resources involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and the study of language corpora (cs.CY).
